    <section id="id1163960971250">
      <title>Memorandum:</title>
      <para id="id1163951362855">Occasions like Entrepreneurs Day or Market Day may be ideal to utilise, as learners get the opportunity to sell their own products and to work with money.</para>
      <list id="id1163960092844" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Learners must design a product to sell on Market Day, e.g. cookies baked at home or decorated bags to put products in. They must first decide which materials they will need and then design / make a simple advertisement on page 11. This is an ideal opportunity to make them aware of expenditure, profit and loss.</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id1163961695626">Let the learners draw a shop-shelf with a variety of products on a A3 page.</para>
    </section>
